&lt;p&gt;Pay by Diners Club card and get&nbsp;an&nbsp;automatic upgrade to a class higher than what you ordered, and at an unbeatable price. This exclusive offer is unlimited in time when renting any car from Sixt in the Czech Republic. The Sixt Exclusive Collection offers luxury limousines, fast sports cars, but also off-road vehicles now also have a special price for Diners Club cardholders. If you show the Sixt Express Card, you can also reach worldwide discounts up to 20% off car rental.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Birthday gift &amp;#8211; Sixt has a special gift for you during&nbsp;your birthday month &amp;#8211; every other day rent free. With the combination discount and Diners Club cardholders can achieve up to 70% off the regular price of the rental.&lt;br /&gt;
Weekend with SIXT takes three days. Sixt Czech Republic brings you a special weekend offer &amp;#8211; Sixt rent a car from Friday to Monday at a bargain price. Valid only for Diners Club cardholders. Must mention reference number &amp;#8220;9814951&amp;#8221; when booking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Offer is applicable only for payments made with Diners Club cards and cannot be combined with any other special offers.&lt;/p&gt;

